{"tid":1639754,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[香港人最多係錢] 隱世眾籌","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:11:27.000Z","uid":30510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b45e53747bc4ee9d614b071b4fac51099932af8e","tid":1639754,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"Gphone twitter出post:<br />\n<code>Hong Kong Democracy Counc is the first-ever organization on Capitol Hill dedicated to the US' support and defense of human rights &amp; democracy in HK the only group led predominately by HKers living in US.</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/us4hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fus4hk&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=37ce755e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/us4hk</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\n<code>\n我哋係香港大專學界國際事務代表團（HKIAD），成立於今年7月。代表團由十二間大專院校學生會代表組成。\n\n我哋曾經喺八月舉辦過「英美港盟主權在民集會」，亦有派出代表去到世界各地進行民間外交及遊說工作。\n\n我哋而家發起眾籌計畫，目標籌款300萬港元，以支援舉行活動、民間外交之費用。\n\n請大家多多支持！\n</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=d0e0f7ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捐之前睇下係唔係同理念<br />\n放上黎只係唔忍心見到無咩人理"},{"pid":"44e41ff82c6a5fcbd8e4b327293d98309f4ed5f3","tid":1639754,"uid":262899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"幫你推～ <br />\n<br />\n幫手推一推～ 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被捕求助（對唔住手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633560</a>"},{"pid":"f55319e8a24964534237c5f9dbdaa442f4952777","tid":1639754,"uid":205826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17